Hey There, and welcome to ThisThat!

We're glad you've decided to join. Here are a few tips to get you started.

1. Connect Your Social Networks
The more networks you connect, the more useful it will be for you.

2. Check your Pending feed
After connecting social networks, you should have some pending posts. Just tag a topic or two and click Share!

3. Explore
The Explore feed shows you what everyone else is sharing - go explore, and don't be afraid to click share on posts you like!

4. Spread the Love
Sharing your ThisThat profile is a great way to showcase everything you're sharing on the web.
Throw a link to your ThisThat profile in your email signature and your Twitter bio!